# ============================================================
# Contactos — Sincronización Google Contacts
# ============================================================

### 1. Generar URL OAuth de Google (solo admin)
GET {{base}}/api/contactos/google/auth
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. URL OAuth con token operativo → 403
GET {{base}}/api/contactos/google/auth
Authorization: Bearer {{token_operativo}}

###

### 3. Estado de la conexión Google
GET {{base}}/api/contactos/google/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Desconectar cuenta Google (solo admin)
DELETE {{base}}/api/contactos/google/conexion
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Leer preferencias de sincronización
GET {{base}}/api/contactos/preferencias
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Guardar preferencias
PUT {{base}}/api/contactos/preferencias
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plantilla": "{FECHA} — {NOMBRE} ({APT})",
  "separador_apt": " / ",
  "formato_fecha_salida": "DD/MM/YYYY"
}

###

### 7. Sincronizar reservas PMS → Google Contacts
POST {{base}}/api/contactos/sincronizacion
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "desde": "2026-05-01",
  "hasta": "2026-05-31"
}

###

### 8. Sincronizar sin PMS configurado → 400
POST {{base}}/api/contactos/sincronizacion
Authorization: Bearer {{token_sin_pms}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "desde": "2026-05-01",
  "hasta": "2026-05-31"
}

###

### 9. Exportar CSV desde PMS (sin Google)
POST {{base}}/api/contactos/exportacion/csv
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "desde": "2026-05-01",
  "hasta": "2026-05-31"
}

###

### 10. Sincronizar desde XLSX → Google Contacts (multipart)
POST {{base}}/api/contactos/xlsx/sincronizacion
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="reservas.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./reservas_ejemplo.xlsx
------Boundary--

###

### 11. Exportar CSV desde XLSX (sin Google)
POST {{base}}/api/contactos/xlsx/exportacion/csv
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="reservas.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./reservas_ejemplo.xlsx
------Boundary--

###

### 12. Exportar CSV sin archivo → 400
POST {{base}}/api/contactos/xlsx/exportacion/csv
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### 13. Empresas — listar (solo superadmin)
GET {{base}}/api/empresas
Authorization: Bearer {{token_superadmin}}

###

### 14. Crear empresa (solo superadmin)
POST {{base}}/api/empresas
Authorization: Bearer {{token_superadmin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Hotel Nuevo S.L.",
  "email": "admin@hotel-nuevo.com"
}

###

### 15. Crear empresa con email duplicado → 409
POST {{base}}/api/empresas
Authorization: Bearer {{token_superadmin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Hotel Nuevo S.L. Copia",
  "email": "admin@hotel-nuevo.com"
}
